    "---\n",
    "## 9. Comparative Baseline Analysis: Physics-Informed Geo-AI vs. Traditional Physical Calibration\n",
    "\n",
    "To quantify the value of Foundation Model embeddings, this section benchmarks the Physics-Informed Geo-AI framework against a **traditional SM2RAIN numerical calibration**. The baseline uses standard L-BFGS-B optimization to fit pixel-level parameters ($Z$, $K$, $b$) independently — without any satellite embedding features.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Comparison Objectives\n",
    "\n",
    "| Objective | Question |\n",
    "|---|---|\n",
    "| **Benchmarking** | How much performance is gained by integrating AlphaEarth embeddings? |\n",
    "| **Generalization** | Does the physics-informed architecture better handle inter-annual variability? |\n",
    "| **Innovation Validation** | Does the framework capture local hydrological signatures beyond what curve-fitting achieves? |"
   ]
  },
